WEBVTT

00:06.548 --> 00:10.664
Hand me the totem, or I will have
one of these men kill you.

00:10.764 --> 00:13.943
Fine! You think I want some crazy
magic totem thing?

00:14.044 --> 00:15.537
It's not my style even.

00:15.637 --> 00:17.701
I just held on to it
for sentimental reasons.

00:17.801 --> 00:19.524
All I wanna know is
where it came from.

00:19.624 --> 00:22.184
You tell me that
and I'll give it to you right now.

00:22.284 --> 00:24.414
I... I can't get it off.

00:24.614 --> 00:26.014
You're lying!

00:26.114 --> 00:27.934
- Oh, no.
- What?

00:28.034 --> 00:29.484
It's bound itself to you.

00:29.584 --> 00:30.705
Fine.

00:30.805 --> 00:33.248
I'll remove it from her corpse.

00:36.711 --> 00:38.238
There!

